IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
    PROGRAM-ID. FullPipelineExample.
    AUTHOR. DataCenter-Ops.
    VERSION. 0-2-0.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    OS "Linux".
    ARCH "x86_64".
    RUNTIME-VERSION "1.0".

DATA DIVISION.
    INPUT VIDEO-MP4 AS RAW-VIDEO.
    INPUT JSON-OBJECT AS METADATA.
    INPUT BINARY-BLOB AS AUDIT-LOG.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    TRANSCODE RAW-VIDEO IMAGE-JPG.
    EXTRACT $.title METADATA.
    VALIDATE METADATA json-schema.
    FILTER AUDIT-LOG has-errors.
    ENCRYPT AUDIT-LOG.
    MERGE RAW-VIDEO,METADATA INTO PACKAGE.
    VERIFY-INTEGRITY PACKAGE.
